  "question": "中国如今的国际地位与苏联相比如何?",
  "author": "呱呱呱",
  "content": "<p>海西女真三十四年，建州兵临辽沈，蒙古犹疑，竟遗满洲半壁于海西。然海西常公暗弱，细喜微操，善日记。三大征皆败，京畿失陷，膏腴之地尽失。海西遂失其鹿，而群雄逐之。德胜位面之子转世，三载余而鼎定天下，破大明，踏准部。</p><p>建州女真即成，蒙古蔑之，欲以父子相称。然建州新立，民气可用，兼有雄主。与蒙古分廷抗礼。</p><p>经年，蒙古铁骑，陈兵百万，建州诸雄，寝食难安。此时蒙古，南援安南，西镇欧洲，东迫东瀛，北至极北。大明视之如仇雠，设蕃镇于五洋，布重兵于四海，核武巡值，日夜不息。蒙古自愎，曰:“吾十七张牌，大明安能秒我。请赐卡布奇诺于大明。”</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-fcc8584f52090ab3a41a085d31489324_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"170\" data-rawheight=\"160\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"170\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;170&#39; height=&#39;160&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"170\" data-rawheight=\"160\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"170\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-fcc8584f52090ab3a41a085d31489324_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p>未几，蒙古暴毙，喀尔喀，察哈尔诸部流离，波罗的海易主。建州为朝贡之事亦自负请罪，废大运，停扩核。大明有学人自叹:“此乃天命昭昭，大明礼法，实乃历史终结。”</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-aeddaec0871acb76b66162576fc5a436_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"492\" data-rawheight=\"308\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0101e569bafd17beeb09a5fc8019135e_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"492\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-aeddaec0871acb76b66162576fc5a436_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;492&#39; height=&#39;308&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"492\" data-rawheight=\"308\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0101e569bafd17beeb09a5fc8019135e_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"492\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-aeddaec0871acb76b66162576fc5a436_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-aeddaec0871acb76b66162576fc5a436_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p>四十载间，韬光养晦，建州势成，气象俨然。然万历三大征亦起，大明无暇东顾。有建州人自比蒙古，然时人笑之，入关之日尚不可知，朝贡尚未断绝，苏松二府，旗人往之，络绎不绝，何来自比蒙古。待分庭抗礼之时，方谈蒙元旧事。他日若得报怨仇，必血染哈德逊河口。诸公谨以自勉。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d713c584046c8ab805cec064aa84a91_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"631\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-efe15b0bc6efdcb10cf929ef11d63371_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8d713c584046c8ab805cec064aa84a91_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;640&#39; height=&#39;631&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"631\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-efe15b0bc6efdcb10cf929ef11d63371_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8d713c584046c8ab805cec064aa84a91_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d713c584046c8ab805cec064aa84a91_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p>本演义纯属扯淡，如有雷同，实属正常</p>",
